Shari L. Burgess

Age : 58Public asset : 269,668 USDLinked companies :  Lear Corporation 





Summary 



Ms. Shari L. Burgess is Treasurer, Chief Diversity Officer & VP at Lear Corp.She is on the Board of Directors at Health Alliance Plan of Michigan. Ms. Burgess was previously employed as Audit Manager by Ernst & Young LLP and Controller by Victor International Corp.



